Package textprocessor

This package provides functionality of the actual text processor.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Helper
    A helper class that contains some useful methods for working with text.
    Patterns
    A class that contains predefined patterns for matching text elements.
    TextOperations
    A class that provides different operations which can be performed on texts.
    TextOperations.SwapFirstLastWordsConsumer
    A Consumer that swaps first and last words in each Sentence of some Text or other collection of TextElement objects.
    TextProcessor
    A class that provides functionality for reading, writing and parsing an epub file.
    TextProcessorDemo
    A demo class.

Package textprocessor Description

This package provides functionality of the actual text processor. It contains classes and methods for reading and writing textual content of epub books, parsing it into Text objects and processing the latter.
